photonicat-pm (1.0.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix battery capacity reporting when PMU firmware RA2E1260306000 reports
    a stuck 100% state of charge while the pack is still charging.
  * Preserve older PMU firmware behavior by only applying the stuck-SOC quirk
    to the affected firmware version.
  * Use the battery design capacity for ENERGY_FULL instead of unsupported PMU
    status report energy fields.
  * Gate PMU behavior through firmware capability profiles and keep /dev/rtc0
    registered while disabling broken RTC and scheduled boot operations on
    RA2E1260306000.

 -- HackingGate <i@hackinggate.com>  Fri, 08 May 2026 20:02:53 +0900

photonicat-pm (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix RTC validity handling for photonicat2 PMU status reporting.
  * Return 0 from RTC set_time() and scheduled boot operations on success.
  * Refresh cached RTC state after successful time synchronization.
  * Prevent stale PMU RTC status bits from incorrectly blocking valid RTC reads.
  * Remove unsupported battery energy_now export from PMU protocol v2.
  * Clarify PMU protocol v2 battery reporting and fan auto-speed restoration
    documentation.
  * Refresh GitHub Actions build, artifact upload, and release actions.
  * Remove obsolete Dependabot auto-merge workflow.

 -- HackingGate <i@hackinggate.com>  Mon, 04 May 2026 15:13:10 +0900

